Aiden Zhane : A lot of people adore her mug but...the outfit is just bleh. The top is cute. It would make a great dress. (I hate her mug) Boot

Brita Filter : That one stripe bedazzled thing across her jacket is weird. So Yee. But overall not too bad. She had great stage presence, Toot

Jan Sport : Looks like a non plastic Gothy Kendall entrance look. She reminds me so much of Gothy, idk why. Boot

Nicky Doll : YASSS MAWMAAAA. SHE CAN BEAT ME UP- The wig, the bat, the chains, everything makes me love it. SHOOT

Rock M Sakura : No, too messy. Boot

Sherry Pie : She reminds me so much of Lady Bunny. I love the curves of the dress. And I love that mug. She serves me camp. Toot

Widow Von Du : She has not impressed me at all, that promo looks sucked, this sucked. I'm assuming he's supposed to be like a mafia leader or something. Whatever it is, I hate it. Boot
